QuestData.Title: Plant Pruning
QuestData.Description: There may be more to this aberrant growth than it seems, but we will need to clear the way a bit before we can get to the bottom of this, yes?$b$bI suggest clearing out some of the angrier defenders to be on the safe side.
QuestData.RewardText: I have slain quite a few as well but they continue to spring up here.$b$bWe will need another solution...
